===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Nate (Masters)}}
Nate, who is based on the [[Battle Subway]] partner, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Braviary}} and {{Shiny}} {{p|Haxorus}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Nate became a playable sync pair on November 12, 2020.

Nate has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

